"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Welcome ðŸ‘‹\\n\\nMy name is Patrick Rivera and I'm a software engineer, writer, and investor in crypto protocols. I currently work at [Mirror](https://mirror.xyz), a protocol helping creators and communities build crypto-native media companies. So far, we've shipped a [decentralized publishing protocol](https://dev.mirror.xyz/J1RD6UQQbdmpCoXvWnuGIfe7WmrbVRdff5EqegO1RjI), [tokenized crowdfunding](https://dev.mirror.xyz/llJ_AboiDJwB_ZAFz-CXU7fL2p8v5Wz6MjfluLafewQ), [NFT auctions](https://dev.mirror.xyz/_OstP6dwYsX-0YsIaGDw-W4fs3VzESC_QpxrhiyM_Bg),  [on-chain revenue splits](https://dev.mirror.xyz/V_7Jp1hy_g8bz-J1B4Wb5KYSmj5Lt4W7q7cw0noxJsU), and a [tokenized referral program](https://mirror.xyz/race).\\n\\nPreviously, I was a growth engineer at [Instacart](https://instacart.com) and a lead growth engineer at a DeFi startup called [Dharma](https://dharma.io).\\n\\nIn my free time, I write about the intersection of crypto, creators, and communities.\\n\\nHere are some of my most popular posts:\\n- [A Presentation on Crypto Fundamentals and NFTs](https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1sUpk0gbvRQelH0MUIOqjNeGe8nwRH4mhrhDHmI6qh4M/edit?usp=sharing)\\n- [Come for the Creator, Stay for the Economy](https://p.mirror.xyz/1EpvJwUpx_KlRcHOKLNqADEkwHL_Z1ZYKobF2uLwgBg)\\n- [Tips for Creators Getting Into Crypto](https://p.mirror.xyz/WQQywdjjfnksMRPMaNKBMxPBqfE5k8nL6pCLe1roGyw)\\n- [Crypto-native Newsletter Businesses](https://p.mirror.xyz/CQnk9PLrBAUskCTCHiA5fA9SBDFZGEfCitVH343FWkY)\\n- [Internet Renaissance Vibez](https://p.mirror.xyz/pl07RMWdJZktHUAn8hZ02YlO35-Ju49orPrhaRnn4Vo)\\n\\nSay hi on [Twitter](https://twitter.com/patrickxrivera) or email me at patrick.x.rivera@gmail.com.\\n\\nI publish a deep dive essay every few weeks so subscribe below to get it right in your inbox.\\n\\nThanks for reading :~)\",\"timestamp\":1623259498,\"title\":\"Start Here\",\"publication\":\"p\"},\"digest\":\"ah1wku3q8kFbeEDs8oieNsvXUljU6Gr_v1U4HjNsPSA\",\"authorship\":{